data.description: URBAN LUXURY IN THE HEART OF NORTH BOULDER! Urban contemporary unit with amazing views of the foothills! This stunning 2 bed + bonus room, 2 bath, 1458 square foot unit has recently underdone a complete remodel! Chef's gourmet kitchen with beautiful gloss walnut cabinets, a large center island with quartz countertops and waterfall edges, new engineered hardwood floors throughout and beautiful stainless steel appliances. The open floor plan is very inviting as the kitchen flows into the dining area and the living room; thus creating a large great room! The open and bright great room with soaring 18+ foot ceilings is accented with a wall of windows and a gas fireplace with Italian marble surround. A spacious private balcony is a one of a kind outdoor oasis in the middle of the city! You can relax and enjoy the breathtaking views of the foothills from your balcony! The newly remodeled primary retreat features a generous size bedroom with a spa-like bathroom with dual sinks, quartz countertops, a large walk-in shower with Euro doors and beautiful walnut gloss built-ins in the oversized walk-in closet. A laundry room and bonus room that can be used as a study or sitting area complete the second level. A few recent updates include new A/C (replaced in 2022), newly remodeled kitchen and bathrooms, newer engineered hardwood floors, newer cabinets and built-ins in primary bedroom closets, new paint and newer fireplace Italian marble surround. An Entertainer's Dream loft style townhouse in a state-of-the-art secure building just steps away from restaurants, shops, parks, trails and so much more! This unit is the epitome of urban luxury at its finest!
